OL,7,FThe parents of a schoolboy who was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death by a fellow pupil
OL,9,Fduring his lunch break said they
OL,10,Fbelieve the school could have saved
OL,11,Fhis life by acting on "too many red
OL,12,Fflags" shown by his killer.
OL,14,FHarvey Willgoose, 15, was murdered in
OL,15,Ffront of horrified children and
OL,16,Fteachers at All Saints Catholic High
OL,17,FSchool in Sheffield by Mohammed Umar
OL,18,FKhan, 15, who took a hunting knife to
OL,19,Fschool.
