OL,7,FAn independent review into Harvey's
OL,8,Fdeath has found "several missed
OL,9,Fopportunities" to address behaviour
OL,10,Fand manage risk before the fatal
OL,11,Fstabbing, the Willgoose family's
OL,12,Flawyers said.
OL,14,FThe private review was commissioned by
OL,15,FSt Clare Catholic Multi Academy Trust,
OL,16,Fwhich runs the school, and undertaken
OL,17,Fby a former school headteacher and
OL,18,Finspector of schools at Learn
OL,19,FSheffield.
