OL,7,FThe trust said it would not be
OL,8,Fpublishing the report because of
OL,9,Fsensitivities involved, but released
OL,10,Fthe recommendations, saying it would
OL,11,Fimplement them in full and had made a
OL,12,Fnumber of changes since Harvey's death
OL,13,Fin February 2025.
OL,15,FSpeaking to reporters ahead of the
OL,16,Fanniversary of Harvey's death on
OL,17,FTuesday, his father Mark Willgoose
OL,18,Fsaid his son's life could "100%" have
OL,19,Fbeen saved by the school.
