OL,7,F"If they were doing what they should
OL,8,Fhave been doing, Harvey would still be
OL,9,Fhere today," he said.
OL,11,FCaroline Willgoose, Harvey's mother,
OL,12,Fsaid the report showed "too many red
OL,13,Fflags" by Khan that were not acted on,
OL,14,Fand renewed her call for knife arches
OL,15,Fto be installed in schools, as she
OL,16,Fsaid children were no safer now than
OL,17,Fat the time of Harvey's death.
OL,19,FShe said: "There's a knife problem out
OL,20,Fthere, the one place children should
OL,21,Ffeel safe is school."
