OL,9,Fand said it found that from the point
OL,10,FKhan was first considered for a move
OL,11,Fto All Saints through to the day of
OL,12,Fthe killing, school leaders "could,
OL,13,Fand at times should, have taken
OL,14,Fdifferent action", with system
OL,15,Fweaknesses contributing to
OL,16,F"oversights, assumptions and
OL,17,Fmisjudgements".
