OL,7,FAccording to Irwin Mitchell, the
OL,8,Freport said safeguarding and behaviour
OL,9,Frecords were not requested or reviewed
OL,10,Fbefore Khan's move from another school
OL,11,Fto All Saints Catholic High was agreed
OL,12,Fand, when later transferred, were not
OL,13,Fread because of unclear responsibility.
OL,15,FThis meant staff were unaware of
OL,16,Fhistoric incidents involving violence,
OL,17,Fweapons references and anger.
OL,19,FIrwin Mitchell said the report also
OL,20,Ffound that weapons-related concerns
OL,21,Fwere handled "inconsistently".
