OL,7,FAfter pupils reported in October 2024
OL,8,Fthat Khan had previously carried a
OL,9,Fknife and brought a BB gun on a school
OL,10,Ftrip, staff carried out a search but
OL,11,Ffailed to investigate further,
OL,12,Fcomplete a risk assessment or put a
OL,13,Fsafety plan in place, and records were
OL,14,Fincomplete.
OL,16,FIn December 2024, when an axe was
OL,17,Ffound in his bag off-site, police were
OL,18,Finformed but no in-school follow-up
OL,19,Foccurred, which the review is said to
OL,20,Fhave described as a safeguarding
OL,21,Ffailure.
