OL,7,FAs Khan's behaviour escalated between
OL,8,FNovember 2024 and January 2025, school
OL,9,Fleaders should have been "joining the
OL,10,Fdots" and recognised these as
OL,11,Fopportunities for intervention, Irwin
OL,12,FMitchell said.
OL,14,FThey added that the report found Khan
OL,15,Fwas allowed into school "unsearched
OL,16,Fand without any completed assessment"
OL,17,Fon the day of Harvey's death despite
OL,18,Fan open investigation into a fresh
OL,19,Fknife allegation.
