OL,7,FThe report sets out 10 recommendations
OL,8,Ffor the school, its Trust, the local
OL,9,Fauthority and the Department for
OL,10,FEducation.
OL,12,FThese include:
OL,14,F` Mandatory record sharing at the
OL,15,Foutset of any pupil school move, with
OL,16,Fsenior sign-off confirming full
OL,17,Fsafeguarding and behaviour records
OL,18,Fhave been reviewed before a pupil
OL,19,Fstarts.
